{"tid":2321850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國財政部未發現金融機構與涉港被制裁人士有重大交易","createTime":"2020-12-12T00:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T01:32:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9824b5aa7e9a56e4746ea68ed5c93199683a03","tid":2321850,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:12:33.000Z","msg":"美國財政部未發現金融機構與涉港被制裁人士有重大交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564916-20201212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564916-20201212.htm&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=2272d9eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564916-20201212.htm&h=a21dc8d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564916-20201212.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部表示，十月中至今，未發現有國際金融機構，故意與被指打壓香港民主而被制裁的人，進行重大交易。<br />\n<br />\n財政部早前宣布，制裁行政長官林鄭月娥等香港與內地官員及前官員，指他們破壞香港自治，限制公民言論及結社自由。國務院要求財政部知會各國際金融機構，指若他們與被列入黑名單的人員交易，將面臨華府制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">財政部強調會持續監察，確保金融機構符合有關準則，並將繼續致力遊說各國政府和國際金融機構，遵從有關措施。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fff9dd9ffa96d04a703da727c532cd19f9d0a420","tid":2321850,"uid":69231,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:19:31.000Z","msg":"即係間間銀行都唔敢做呢班人生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔怪之得要現金出糧<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmOwQnN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmOwQnN.jpg&h=60c24591&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df85a8ad9d8149d7db20423ac21ac1a7b15a200c","tid":2321850,"uid":104592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"姐係果幾個狗官都係出cash <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都幾十萬<br />\n<br />\n成屋都係現金 又要換大間d <br />\n<br />\n買樓賣樓都cash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8f6c210ee8eda0419b1bb1635f6e510291650b","tid":2321850,"uid":106026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"銀行係咪犯咗國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197205760a038aba614c012419a5f76171e759bd","tid":2321850,"uid":49685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:50:19.000Z","msg":"你唔俾人哋有第二個身份用嚟出糧咩？<br />\n慢慢走都有幾本特衰護照啦！"},{"pid":"3e6f56f3c9f351692911dcd96c1386a5ea41c4f1","tid":2321850,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"即係戴咗幾層白手套啦"},{"pid":"57dba211357895165ccd85f34fa384f84ddb39e6","tid":2321850,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"厲害了支那狗，一啲都唔驚美帝制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9830a26f7679dc8b92a1a152afc9a9bf5ebd6fa6","tid":2321850,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e6f56f3c9f351692911dcd96c1386a5ea41c4f1","tid":2321850,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"即係戴咗幾層白手套啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"保安局長叫入境處長開個臨時ID用有幾難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f593508a4cb8ed43f75e7e128e4dfc51f7b04cd","tid":2321850,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9830a26f7679dc8b92a1a152afc9a9bf5ebd6fa6","tid":2321850,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e6f56f3c9f351692911dcd96c1386a5ea41c4f1","tid":2321850,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"即係戴咗幾層白手套啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"保安局長叫入境處長開個臨時ID用有幾難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\